name: Ordinary City Life #1
description:
Through photography, I have frequently captured city lives. With various mind frames, I like to use an approach of urbanized ‘landscape photography’ as an articulation of my works.

Through the works I show my interest in a situation that often seen ‘emotionless’ – when admiration and absurdity become inseparable. 

For me, a big city along with its rapid changes and the problems followed together with these shifts are already taken as our daily realities. Despite the presence of, ‘disappointment’ and absurdity, these realities are always fascinating in strange ways.
